      "text": "Peeztem/luhdsams/man-\nnu Swehtibu/kaſtew peevesta\nirr/ jo Deews irr man to ſehhli-\ngi eedahwanajis / un man irr\nDeews un gann: Un tas ſpeede\nwiſſu/ ka wiſſch to nehine.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſch fazzija : Nahz/\ncima prohjam/ es eefchu ar tew\nlihdſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tas fazzija us wiſſu:\nMans Kungs ſinn/ ka man mihe-\nſti Behrni un Awis/ un ſihda-\nmas Gohwis irr/ kad tohs twee-\nnu Deenu tiffai pahrdſihtu/ tad\nman wiſſi Lohpini apmirtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eij Kungs/luhdsams/ ta-\nwam Kalpam papreeſſchu/ un es\nwaddifchu wahtiain/itt ka man-\nnas Leetas/ kas preeſſch man irr/\npaspehj/ un itt ka tee Behrni pa-\nspehj/ teekams es pee mannu\nKungu Seira nahku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Eesaws fazzija : Es\ntad jelle painettifchu pee tew zit-\ntus/ no teem Laudim / kaſ pee\nman irr/ un tas fazzija : Kam\nwaijaga / laid es Schehlaſtibu\natrohnu/ manna Kunga Azzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta atgreeſahs Eesaws\ntanni Deenâ/ pa fawu Zeltu us\nSeiru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Jehkabs nogahje uhs\nSukotu/ un uszehle Namnu\npreeſſch ſewim / un darrija fa-\nweim Lohpeem Laidarus/ tadeht\nnotanze wiſſch tahs Weetas\nWahrdn Sukot.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs nahze uhs\nSalemu / Sikeema Pilſſahtu /\nkaſ irr eeſſch Kanana Semmes\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nopirkahs weenu Sem-\nmes Gabbalu/ no Eemora Behr-\nneim/ Sikeema Tehwa/ par ſimte\nSudraba Gabbaleem/ un uszeh-\nle tur fawu Dſihwokli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un uſtaisija tur weenu Al-\ntari/un noſauze to: TasSPEH-\nZIGAIS irr Israeta Deewg\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kad wiſſch no Mesopotamijae\nnahze/ un apmettehs preeſſch ta-\nPilſfahta.\n"
    }
  ],
